The paper discusses the properties of polyhedra, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The concept of dihedral angles is also relevant to the study of geometric representations of graphs (cs.GR). The paper also involves exploring the properties of polyhedra using combinatorial methods (cs.DM). Additionally, the paper may be relevant to the study of optimization problems involving polyhedra (cs.MG) and the development of algorithms for geometric computations (cs.SI).
